A minimalistic composition featuring a single elegant penguin silhouette standing confidently atop a sleek, translucent cube that contains swirling abstract layers suggesting virtualization and nested environments. The cube hovers above a clean gradient surface shifting from deep arctic blue to soft white. Inside the cube, subtle geometric patterns hint at contained operating systems and digital architecture. The penguin casts a long, dramatic shadow that fragments into multiple smaller platform shapes. Clean lines, limited color palette of blues, whites, and subtle grays, with sharp contrast and plenty of negative space creating a sophisticated, modern aesthetic.
